COMMENT ON FUNCTION public.delete_reception_entry_cascade(p_id bigint) IS 'Deletes a service_reception_entries row and all dependents in safe order. Blocks if a bodyshop repair card with a real DMS job card number exists. Returns storage paths for client-side bucket cleanup.';


